<bibRefCitation author="Cooper, K. W." box="[864,1031,1627,1654]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="36 - 40" refId="ref46942" refString="Cooper, K. W. (1967) Picromerus bidens (Linn.), a beneficial, predatory European bug discovered in Vermont (Heteroptera: Pentatomidae). Entomological News, 78 (2), 36 - 40." type="journal article" year="1967">Cooper (1967)</bibRefCitation>
